rtert, taktische Hinweise, Beispielsfälle und Formulierungsvorschläge runden die Darstellung ab.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 7aLAW / Business & Financial.2bisacsh1 aZabel, Karsten, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2015 Part 2z978311076664608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2015z9783110438703oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97838145546310 cprintz978381459017240uhttps://doi.org/10.15375/978381455752640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783814557526423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783814557526/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-076664-6  DG Plus PP Package 2015 Part 2b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2015  aZDB-23-DGGb2015